background:white;text-autospace:none'><b><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
color:black'>7.5. Метод исследования операций</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:134.7pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
63.75pt;background:white;text-autospace:none'><i><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
color:black'>&nbsp;</span></i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:134.7pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
63.75pt;background:white;text-autospace:none'><i><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
color:black'>Если у тебя спрошено будет:</span></i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:134.7pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
63.75pt;background:white;text-autospace:none'><i><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
color:black'>что полезнее, солнце или месяц —</span></i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:134.7pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
63.75pt;background:white;text-autospace:none'><i><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
color:black'>ответствуй: месяц.</span></i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:134.7pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
63.75pt;background:white;text-autospace:none'><i><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
color:black'>Ибо солнце светит днем,</span></i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:134.7pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
63.75pt;background:white;text-autospace:none'><i><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
